Description: Modern Go backend for contact form processing
 This is a modern Go backend implementation that replaces a PHP contact
 form handler. The application processes contact form submissions with
 validation, reCAPTCHA verification, and email sending.
 .
 Key features:
  - Form field validation matching frontend regex patterns
  - Google reCAPTCHA v3 validation with configurable score threshold
  - SMTP email sending with TLS
  - Rate limiting to prevent spam
  - Graceful shutdown with signal handling
  - Structured logging
  - JSON API responses
  - Security best practices
  - Systemd integration for easy deployment
